                <p>
                    <lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi> <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> vikkiramacoḻa<hi rend="grantha">de</hi>vaṟku yāṇṭu 8 Āvatu coḻa maṇṭalattu naṭuviṟ kūṟṟu kaṅkai koṇṭacoḻapurattu maṉṟāṭi ceṭṭan tiruvāṟai <hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>yaṅkoṇṭaco
                    <lb n="2" break="no"/>ḻamaṇṭalattu māttūr nāṭṭut tiruvakkarai Āḻvāṟku vaitta <hi rend="grantha">sandhi</hi>viḷakku Onṟukku viṭṭa vāṭu paṉniraṇṭu Ivvāṭu <num value="12"><g type="numeral">10</g> 2</num>m kaikkoṇṭen
                    <lb n="3"/>Ikkoyil kāṇi Uṭaiya kulaṅkiḻavan <hi rend="grantha">Āttre</hi>yan tirunāṭuṭaiyā<supplied reason="omitted">ṉeṉ</supplied>
                </p>
                
